transcript:
Customer: Haan ji.
Executive: Haan ji sir bataye. Hello.
Customer: Haan hello. Haan ji madam.
Executive: Bataye sir.
Customer: Apne wale mein kya hua madam bataiye aap.
Executive: Apke wale mein sir Atul sir se baat hui thi to sir se Saddam sir se.
Customer: Kis se hui?
Executive: Saddam. Kis se hui thi meri baat?
Customer: Apki Atul sir se hui thi Saddam sir se.
Customer: Achcha wo apna kaam nahi hua tha baat karne se kaam hota hai kya? Matlab baat aap jaise kar lo kaam ho jayega kya?
Executive: Nahi.
Customer: Baat to aap bhi kar rahe ho humse.
Customer: Aap ya aap humse baat karte kaam hota hai kya?
Customer: Kaam nahi hua na apna kaam ki kab hua ye batao aap.
Executive: Sir aap buyer wala jo issue bata rahe hain conversion nahi ho pa raha hai buyer ki. Kahan hai buyer wala bataiye kahan hai buyer wala apne bhai ground nut mein karne thi ground nut mein kahan hai bataiye aap.
Customer: Ground nut ki lead aapko nahi hai.
Customer: Ji kahan hai bataiye aap.
Executive: Ground nut ki lead apne apne package liye do mahine bhar ho gaya usme kya lead aayi hai bataiye aap hume.
Executive: Sir leads to ja hi rahi hai aapke usme profile pe daily basis mein work chal raha hai. To aapko malum hai kya wo lead genuine hai?
Executive: Fir wo lead le lenge to genuine fir wo lead le lenge genuine aayegi fir wo kahan se lenge fir?
Executive: Ab kya genuine buyer ka yahi hota hai na abhi jinhone requirement post ki hai unko itna chahiye hoga tabhi to unhone post ki hai. 10 kilo 20 kilo dal denge kya usko?
Customer: Nahi.
Executive: 1 kilo 2 kilo dal denge usko?
Executive: Nahi nahi hum to aapki profile pe 10 wali lead se jyada se jyada provide karate hain jaisa aap consume karte hain 10 wala.
Customer: To fir?
Executive: Ji ab aapka tha 10 wala issue to aapko batao India India mart pe India mart pe aise hi kaam hota hai kya? Saal mein ya ek buyer aata hai ya saal mein do buyer aate hai itne kaam hota hai kya?
Executive: Nahi nahi sir aisa kaam nahi hota. Abdul sir se baat kare hume.
Customer: Unko bole humse baat kare.
Executive: Ji ji Abdul sir se bolte hain. Sir ye.
Customer: Hello.
Customer: Haan ji bhaiya.
Executive: Ji sir.
Customer: Kya Abdul bhaiya apna kya hua hai ye ye ground nut wala apne paas mein aa hi nahi raha hai koi lead. Aap aise phone karo main apne wale number se. Aap apne wale number se phone karo hume.
Executive: Sir aapne customer care pe call kar diya hai sir aap customer care pe maine aapko bola tha na ki direct mujhse baat karne ke liye Saddam sir se bhi baat. Aap hume aap hume phone kijiye aap wale number se.
Executive: Mere number number pe kahan call kiya hai aapne customer
